Functions, program calls

  polyaspwm_predict.pl seq.fa

            Standard PAS prediction producing a *.csv format list

  polyastrain_call_predict.sh seq.fa

            The same standard prediction as with polyaspwm.pl, but doing live
            prediction using PWM engine.

  polyaspwm_predict.pl seq.fa | polyaspwm_scorenimg.sh

            Format predictions to candidate density plot. Output is *.png
            format image.


External program ressources

  PWMscanNt - package pwmsuite, K Szafranski
            PWM engine for live prediction.

  seqct   - package seqhdl, K Szafranski
            Needed for live prediction using PWM engine.
            Any other tool for seq length determination may step in, here

  Plot.pl - package kPerl, K Szafranski
            for visualization via polyaspwm.pl (or polyas_call_polyaspwm.sh)

